                "string_values": [
                  "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Aumenta l'efficacia dello scudo di un</span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\"> 20%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">25%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">30%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">35%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">40%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">. Mandare a segno un colpo contro gli avversari aumenta l'</span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">ATT</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> di un </span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">4%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">5%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">6%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">7%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">8%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> per </span><span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">8 s</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">. </span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Cumulabile fino a 5 volte</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">. Si può verificare una sola volta ogni </span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">0,3 s</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">. Mentre la protezione dello </span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">scudo</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> è attiva, l'effetto di quest'</span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">ATT</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> aumenta di un </span><span style=\"color: #37FFFF\">100%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">.</span></p>"
